---
import ZhLayout from '../../../../layouts/ZhLayout.astro';
---

<ZhLayout
  title="精密加工零件 | DGSDK 史帝克"
  description="史帝克高精度CNC加工零件：定制铣削、车削和精密加工零件，稳定公差控制，适用于工业设备集成和结构支撑。"
  canonical="https://www.dg-sdk.com/zh/products/precision-machined-parts"
>
  <section
    class="products-hero"
    style="background: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.28), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18)), url('/assets/img/cleaning-machine/cnc-parts.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;"
  >
    <div class="container products-hero-inner">
      <span class="products-hero-kicker">史帝克产品系列</span>
      <h1>精密加工零件</h1>
      <p>
        高精度CNC加工零件，稳定公差控制，用于工业设备集成、结构支撑及精密制造应用。
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="products-overview-section">
    <div class="container products-overview-layout">
      <aside class="products-sidebar">
        <div class="products-sidebar-box">
          <h3>产品分类</h3>
          <a href="/zh/products">所有产品</a>
          <a href="/zh/products/static-eliminator">静电消除系统</a>
          <a href="/zh/products/cleaning-machine">工业清洁机</a>
          <a href="/zh/products/precision-machined-parts" class="active-category">精密加工零件</a>
          <a href="/zh/products/automation">自动化设备</a>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <div class="products-main">
        <section class="apple-product-section">
          <div class="apple-card-grid">
            <a href="/zh/products/precision-machined-parts/custom-precision-machined-parts" class="apple-product-card">
              <img src="/assets/img/precision-machined-parts/precision-machined-parts.jpg" alt="定制精密加工零件" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="apple-card-tag">精密零件</span>
              <h3>定制精密加工零件</h3>
              <p>根据客户图纸和规格定制的高精度CNC加工零件。</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/zh/products/precision-machined-parts/cnc-milled-front-panel-rubber-roller-assembly" class="apple-product-card">
              <img src="/assets/img/precision-machined-parts/cnc-milled-front-panel-rubber-roller-assembly.jpg" alt="CNC铣削前面板橡胶辊组件" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="apple-card-tag">精密零件</span>
              <h3>CNC铣削前面板橡胶辊组件</h3>
              <p>用于滚轮应用的精密铣削面板和辊组件。</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/zh/products/precision-machined-parts/cnc-wing-connection-block" class="apple-product-card">
              <img src="/assets/img/precision-machined-parts/cnc-milled-wing-connection-block.jpg" alt="CNC翼型连接块" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="apple-card-tag">精密零件</span>
              <h3>CNC翼型连接块</h3>
              <p>用于设备集成的高精度结构连接块。</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/zh/products/precision-machined-parts/lathe-machined-bearing-outer-retainer-plate" class="apple-product-card">
              <img src="/assets/img/precision-machined-parts/lathe-machined-bearing-outer-retainer-plate.jpg" alt="车床加工轴承外圆固定板" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="apple-card-tag">精密零件</span>
              <h3>车床加工轴承外圆固定板</h3>
              <p>高精度车床加工，保障轴承系统的稳定固定。</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/zh/products/precision-machined-parts/lathe-machined-shaft-end-fixing-component" class="apple-product-card">
              <img src="/assets/img/precision-machined-parts/lathe-machined-shaft-end-fixing-component.jpg" alt="车床加工轴端固定件" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="apple-card-tag">精密零件</span>
              <h3>车床加工轴端固定件</h3>
              <p>用于轴端定位和固定的精密车削零件。</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/zh/products/precision-machined-parts/milled-front-inner-fixing-plate-paper-roll-guide-rail" class="apple-product-card">
              <img src="/assets/img/precision-machined-parts/milled-front-inner-fixing-plate-paper-roll-guide-rail.jpg" alt="铣削前内固定板纸卷导轨" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="apple-card-tag">精密零件</span>
              <h3>铣削前内固定板纸卷导轨</h3>
              <p>用于纸卷和物料引导应用的精密铣削导轨组件。</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/zh/products/precision-machined-parts/precision-bearing-bracket-cnc-milled" class="apple-product-card">
              <img src="/assets/img/precision-machined-parts/precision-bearing-bracket-cnc-milled.jpg" alt="精密轴承支架（CNC铣削）" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="apple-card-tag">精密零件</span>
              <h3>精密轴承支架（CNC铣削）</h3>
              <p>高精度CNC铣削轴承支架，公差稳定可靠。</p>
            </a>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="related-categories-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="related-cat-title">探索更多解决方案</h2>
      <p class="related-cat-desc">精密零件通常与清洁机和自动化设备配套使用。了解我们的相关产品类别：</p>
      <div class="related-cat-grid">
        <a href="/zh/products/cleaning-machine" class="related-cat-card">
          <img src="/assets/img/cleaning-machine/polarizer-cleaner.jpg" alt="工业清洁机" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="related-cat-info">
            <h3>工业清洁机</h3>
            <p>PCB、FPC、光学薄膜及SMT应用的精密清洁设备。</p>
            <span class="related-cat-link">查看产品 →</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/zh/products/automation" class="related-cat-card">
          <img src="/assets/img/automation/product-a.jpg" alt="自动化设备" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="related-cat-info">
            <h3>自动化设备</h3>
            <p>定制自动化系统，提升工作流程和生产效率。</p>
            <span class="related-cat-link">查看产品 →</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/zh/products/static-eliminator" class="related-cat-card">
          <img src="/assets/img/static-eliminator/st-g.jpg" alt="静电消除系统" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="related-cat-info">
            <h3>静电消除系统</h3>
            <p>适用于精密制造和工业生产线的专业静电控制设备。</p>
            <span class="related-cat-link">查看产品 →</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ZhLayout>
